n of the kinetic-energy expectation value exhibits a relatively slow\nquantum-diffusive behavior having universal features. These approximate\nspectral and quantum-dynamical universalities agree with predictions from the\neffective Hamiltonian.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Apr 2018 21:32:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-08"}
