e state-of-the-art algorithms and improve the\nperformance across all the applications that we consider.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Apr 2018 07:09:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Jul 2018 14:11:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-05"}
